data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully updated condo in desirable Highland Creek! Step inside the spacious great room featured with cathedral ceilings & cozy gas fireplace to enjoy just in time for the Holidays! The large arched windows accompanied with the open floor plan boasts natural light throughout. This unit is unique with a larger sunroom that is both heated & cooled, providing the perfect atmosphere to relax & entertain throughout all seasons. Completely updated kitchen with new cabinets, granite counter tops, backsplash, & SS appliances. Ample counter space, cabinets, & pantry creates the ideal setting to prepare any meal! The split floor plan provides a primary suite with tray ceilings, large walk-in closet & updated bathroom, paired with two guest bedrooms. Two car garage has attic access & large cabinets for storage. This community has tons of amenities, monthly activities & within minutes to shopping & I-485.
